# Netlify redirects + proxy rules
# https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/

# Proxy CelesTrak TLE feed through our own origin so the browser
# fetch is same-origin (no CORS preflight, no network policy hassle).
# Status 200 means it rewrites the response in place rather than
# sending a 3xx. The :group placeholder captures any constellation
# group key — "starlink", "oneweb", "gps-ops", etc.
/api/tle/:group  https://celestrak.org/NORAD/elements/gp.php?GROUP=:group&FORMAT=tle  200
